@Mario Ishikawa 
1. The answer is sort of -- you can create components, but it is best to use the Ignition sdk to this as you will want to expose all of the event handlers and api methods with your component.
2. You can use an iframe, yes, but the component object will be the browser or iframe component and not your chart (so events on the chart are not exposed to the rest of the environment).

